HEADWORD: Nosebag
<hw>Nose"bag`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A bag in which feed
for a horse, ox, or the like, may be fastened under the nose by a string
passing over the head.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

